title: Deciding What to Eat
description:
Written by Kristy Lopez-Bernal
Starring: Langan Kingsley, Lisa Kleinman, Kelly Hudson, Kerry O'Brien, Alene Latimer

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, September 23, 2013.
